title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Your enthusiasm compels you to tackle something thats been on your mind for a long time. But dont attempt to bite off more than you can handle today. Paradoxically, narrowing your focus enables you to complete a body of work that makes you proud. Be content just to start with even a small part of a larger endeavor. Your immediate task might not stroke your ego, but youre trying to stoke a lasting triumph. Entrepreneur Bill Gates said, Most people overestimate what they can do in one year and underestimate what they can do in ten years. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
